    <section_number>6</section_number>
    <catch_line>Lawful Possession Not Taxable</catch_line>
    <order_by>6</order_by>
    <text>
        Nothing in this chapter shall be construed to require persons lawfully in possession of marihuana or a controlled substance to pay the tax required pursuant to this chapter.
